reviews.text: Good place with good dimsum. The prices are acceptable and fine. Wait could take a while and there are not enough seats for waiting. Many elderly people have to stand for 30 minutes.

Great place to have a large variety of dim sum. However come by before 11am because they have a few selection of dim sum exclusively during early morning to 11am. After 11am, they have a lunch special menu. Most special dishes are in Chinese so bonus if you can read them.
Cozy place, nice dim sum and good service.
The perfect place for dim sum. The air conditioning is a little cold so bring a jumper. Very good service so I go frequently when I'm in Hong Kong.
good dim sim

reviews.text: 場地大，服務好，餐點口味不錯，適合朋友聚會
環境不错，食物尚佳，價格稍贵。
交通方便，環境優雅。吃的中上價，味道有水準，服務也OK。埸地寛廣，適合婚宴或公司團驟。
新裝修後，點心飲茶都好食。特別推介點心紙的點心都可以試。
進入了花花世界！完全不似傳統中式酒樓

reviews.text: 服務態度欠佳，例子 : 向服務員取B B椅，說了三次也沒有理會，進食過程中叫服務員加水冲茶，她提起在檯面上的熱水壺，然後說壼裡面還有水就走了(但壼裏面並沒有太多水，而水也不夠熱)。食物器皿不夠清潔，而食物質素只是一般。
食物水平Ok，視野(望維園)廣濶，服務也算有條理，但冷氣特勁，注意！
Good place with good dimsum. The prices are acceptable and fine. Wait could take a while and there are not enough seats for waiting. Many elderly people have to stand for 30 minutes.
早茶價錢便宜、抵吃！
食物不錯，檯布及食具有污漬
